<preface xml:id="PsiReference_Introduction">
<title>Preface</title>

<para>
Ψ is an interpreted scripting programming language whose syntax is based on
PostScript® language.
</para>

<para>
Ψ interpreter is programmed in Java. It is possible to extend the language
with both new operators and new types, as well as embedding the interpreter in
Java applications.
</para>

