<para>
This reference describes the algorithmic language, very similar to PostScript.
It is based on the books <link
xlink:href="https://www.adobe.com/products/postscript/pdfs/PLRM.pdf">PostScript®
Language Reference (third edition)</link> and <link
xlink:href="http://partners.adobe.com/public/developer/en/ps/psrefman.pdf">PostScript
Language Reference Manual (second edition)</link>. The reference structure, the
description of the language and operators are largely borrowed from these
sources. We thank the writers of Adobe Systems Incorporated for the excellent
books.
